## OmitBy type

Omit all properties of given type in object type

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
declare type OmitProperties<T, P> = Pick<
  T,
  {
    [K in keyof T]: T[K] extends P ? never : K;
  }[keyof T]
>;
```
